  "body": "Currently the state transition is a synchronous function, this leads to problems when many epochs are processed at once, since we cannot perform any other tasks (eg: respond to network requests).\n\nCreate a worker thread that will process the state transition if block.message.slot - state.slot > MAX_SYNC_SLOTS.",
